OL,3,CJersey's living wage to increase in
OL,4,C2025
OL,6,FJersey's living wage is set to
OL,7,Fincrease for next year.
OL,9,FThe new rate will be #14.13 per hour,
OL,10,Fwith the charity Caritas saying that
OL,11,Fthe living wage has never been as
OL,12,Fimportant, particularly given a
OL,13,Fcontinuing rise in foodbank usage.
OL,15,FThe sum is very similar to two thirds
OL,16,Fof 2024's median wage of #14.17 - the
OL,17,Frate which the States Assembly wants
OL,18,Fto reach.
